      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is sound, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has seen regular oil changes. The interior is clean, featuring well-preserved upholstery with only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. On the exterior, the paint retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side door. All electronics, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. It\u2019s a dependable car that\u2019s ready for the road with no immediate repairs needed.",
